## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Since this is a UI prototype focused on answering the user question, we will verify correct compilation of `lib/main.dart` by running Flutter's build tool or checker.

### Manual Verification
- We will launch the Flutter app in web-server mode using `flutter run -d web-server` (if Flutter SDK is available on PATH or can be invoked) or build it, and check layout using the browser subagent.
- Alternatively, we will perform static code analysis to guarantee a 100% error-free build.
